name: UNCEASING VIXEN 14:46
description: A vision of entangled ecstasy. Two vixens are a sight not easily forgotten by the vigorous masculine spirit. They are interwoven with a gentle caress and unceasing endearment. Coupled vixens are always better than one. Stacked intoxication is always grander than solitary euphoria.  Blessedness on the part of an intrepid rapture fills the air with the sweet perfume of inlaid sweetness.  We waltz to the beat of a triptych within our desire. From the exterior, you gaze at a beauty far from the realm of illustration.  You sit silent wishing for the surreal state of betrothal, amongst the elegance.  Allure has condemned you to a state of restlessness only solved with solace.
